SELECT course_id, temperature FROM golf_course_weather_data WHERE date = '2022-10-15';
SELECT date, precipitation FROM golf_course_weather_data WHERE temperature > 25;
SELECT * FROM golf_course_weather_data ORDER BY temperature DESC;
SELECT AVG(temperature) AS avg_temp, MAX(precipitation) AS max_precip FROM golf_course_weather_data;
SELECT * FROM golf_course_weather_data WHERE temperature > 80 AND precipitation = 0.5 ORDER BY date DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT course_id, AVG(temperature) AS avg_temp FROM golf_course_weather_data GROUP BY course_id ORDER BY avg_temp DESC

SELECT course_id, COUNT(*) AS total_records FROM golf_course_weather_data GROUP BY course_id HAVING total_records > 5 ORDER BY course_id
